1.2
- prevent unauthorized person submit ticket via email via PostMaster*.pl
- improve search with ticket-free-key (dropdown and free text field)!!
- remove header/footer of spelling window
- add config option for Kernel/Modules/*.pm if ticket need to be locked,
   or will be unlocked, ...
- change time column format of time_accounting table from int to
   float(6,2) - http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2003-April/001480.html
- add preferences 'number of default tickets shown in QueueView'
- Write email (new ticket) to customer 
   http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2003-April/001377.html
- Add TicketHookSpace -> e. g. ": " or ""
- merge tickets -
   http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2002-August/000147.html (martin)
- send bulk answer -
   http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2002-June/000066.html (martin)
- delete option for records (martin)
- improve ticket search with between x and y
- add attachment option to phone view
- contact customer -=> create ticket
- customer group feature
- add info that a ticket is already closed!

2.0
